data.description: SELLERS WILL GIVE $3,000 TOWARDS THE BUYERS CLOSING COSTS WITH FULL PRICE OFFER!!! $6K WHOLE HOUSE WATER FILTRATION SYSTEM INCLUDED!!! This inviting two-story townhome features three bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing a comfortable and stylish living space. The open kitchen is a highlight, showcasing beautiful granite countertops, large kitchen cabinets finished with beautiful hardware, stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry, and a central island with a sink. This townhouse has some amazing finishing touches that includes, plantation shutters, crown molding wine storage rack in the kitchen and a hide away garbage storage drawer. The great room, adorned with wood tile finish floors, seamlessly connects to a screened lanai, offering a delightful space to relax. The master bedroom provides a luxurious retreat that includes a glass-enclosed shower. The double vanity with granite countertop, linen closet, and walk-in closet enhance the master suite's functionality. On the second floor, two secondary bedrooms share a well-appointed private bathroom. The main level includes a convenient powder room for residents and guests. Outdoor entertainment is made easy with an extended patio. Additionally, the townhome is strategically located, less than 20min away from Tampa Premium Outlets, making it convenient for residents to access various amenities. If the beautiful gulf of Mexico is calling your name, you are just 30 min from Tarpon Springs and its amazing lifestyle with the best Greek cuisine Florida has to offer. If golf is your game, drive 10min to TPC Tampa Bay golf course, it is gorgeous! Take the 275 south and you are 30 min from the heart of it all, downtown Tampa and all of its amenities. Furthermore, it's just a little over a mile from Publix, adding another layer of accessibility for everyday needs. Call today and don’t let this one get away!!!
